<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.4.2">
<l>poṟṟoṭittōḷ maṭamakaḷtaṉ vaṭivu koṇṭa pollāta vaṉpēycci koṅkai vāṅki</l>
<l>peṟṟeṭutta tāypōla maṭuppa vārum pēṇānañ cuṇṭukanta piḷḷai kaṇṭīr</l>
<l>neṟṟoṭutta malarnīlam niṟainta cūḻa liruñciṟaiya vaṇṭoliyum neṭuṅka ṇārtam</l>
<l>ciṟṟaṭimēl cilampoliyum miḻaṟṟu nāṅkūrt tirutteṟṟi yampalatteṉ ceṅkaṇ mālē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The child who was satisfied, having eaten the poison</l>
<l rend="indent">that no one would swallow when he suckled,</l>
<l rend="indent">like [with] a mother who begot [and] raised him,</l>
<l>Taking the breast of the vicious, evil demoness who took the form</l>
<l rend="indent">of a simple woman with gold bangles on her arms, you see,</l>
<l>Is my bright-eyed Māl in Tirutteṟṟiyampalam in Nāṅkūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">its surroundings filled with blue lily flowers packed in the paddy,</l>
<l>Where whisper the sounds of black-winged bees</l>
<l rend="indent">and the sounds of [ankle] bells on little feet of long-eyed girls.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
